text: Kitchel is an unincorporated community in Harrison Township, Union County, in the U.S. state of Indiana. ==History== A post office was established at Kitchel in 1901, and remained in operation until it was discontinued in 1951. ==Geography== Kitchel is located at . ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Union County, Indiana Category:Unincorporated communities in Indiana
